#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.11:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.11:0.2"
msgid "2. Caravagga "
msgstr "2. Walking "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: carantasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Carasutta "
msgstr "11. Walking "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.11:1.1"
msgid "“Carato cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose a mendicant has a sensual, malicious, or cruel thought while walking. "

#. VAR: byantīkaroti → vyantikaroti (pts1) | byantiṃ karoti (mr)
msgctxt "an4.11:1.2"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu adhivāseti, nappajahati na vinodeti na byantīkaroti na anabhāvaṃ gameti, carampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘anātāpī anottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ kusīto hīnavīriyo’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "They tolerate it and don’t give it up, get rid of it, eliminate it, and obliterate it. Such a mendicant is said to be ‘not keen or prudent, always lazy, and lacking energy’ when walking. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.11:2.1"
msgid "Ṭhitassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā. "
msgstr "Suppose a mendicant has a sensual, malicious, or cruel thought while standing … "

msgctxt "an4.11:2.2"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu adhivāseti, nappajahati na vinodeti na byantīkaroti na anabhāvaṃ gameti, ṭhitopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘anātāpī anottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ kusīto hīnavīriyo’ti vuccati. "
msgstr " "

#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.11:3.1"
msgid "Nisinnassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā. "
msgstr "sitting … "

msgctxt "an4.11:3.2"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu adhivāseti, nappajahati na vinodeti na byantīkaroti na anabhāvaṃ gameti, nisinnopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘anātāpī anottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ kusīto hīnavīriyo’ti vuccati. "
msgstr " "

#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.11:4.1"
msgid "Sayānassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno jāgarassa uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā. "
msgstr "or when lying down while awake. "

msgctxt "an4.11:4.2"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu adhivāseti, nappajahati na vinodeti na byantīkaroti na anabhāvaṃ gameti, sayānopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu jāgaro evaṃbhūto ‘anātāpī anottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ kusīto hīnavīriyo’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "They tolerate it and don’t give it up, get rid of it, eliminate it, and obliterate it. Such a mendicant is said to be ‘not keen or prudent, always lazy, and lacking energy’ when lying down while awake. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.11:5.1"
msgid "Carato cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā. "
msgstr "Suppose a mendicant has a sensual, malicious, or cruel thought while walking. "

msgctxt "an4.11:5.2"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu nādhivāseti, pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti; "
msgstr "They don’t tolerate it, but give it up, get rid of it, eliminate it, and obliterate it. "

msgctxt "an4.11:5.3"
msgid "carampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘ātāpī ottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ āraddhavīriyo pahitatto’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "Such a mendicant is said to be ‘keen and prudent, always energetic and determined’ when walking. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an4.11:6.1"
msgid "Ṭhitassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā. "
msgstr "Suppose a mendicant has a sensual, malicious, or cruel thought while standing … "

msgctxt "an4.11:6.2"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu nādhivāseti, pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.11:6.3"
msgid "ṭhitopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘ātāpī ottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ āraddhavīriyo pahitatto’ti vuccati. "
msgstr " "

#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an4.11:7.1"
msgid "Nisinnassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā. "
msgstr "sitting … "

msgctxt "an4.11:7.2"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu nādhivāseti, pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.11:7.3"
msgid "nisinnopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘ātāpī ottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ āraddhavīriyo pahitatto’ti vuccati. "
msgstr " "

#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.14, sc8
msgctxt "an4.11:8.1"
msgid "Sayānassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno jāgarassa uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā. "
msgstr "or when lying down while awake. "

msgctxt "an4.11:8.2"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu nādhivāseti, pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti; "
msgstr "They don’t tolerate it, but give it up, get rid of it, eliminate it, and obliterate it. "

msgctxt "an4.11:8.3"
msgid "sayānopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu jāgaro evaṃbhūto ‘ātāpī ottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ āraddhavīriyo pahitatto’ti vuccatīti. "
msgstr "Such a mendicant is said to be ‘keen and prudent, always energetic and determined’ when lying down while awake.” "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an4.11:9.1"
msgid "Caraṃ vā yadi vā tiṭṭhaṃ, "
msgstr "Whether walking or standing, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:9.2"
msgid "nisinno uda vā sayaṃ; "
msgstr "sitting or lying down, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:9.3"
msgid "Yo vitakkaṃ vitakketi, "
msgstr "if you think a bad thought "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:9.4"
msgid "pāpakaṃ gehanissitaṃ. "
msgstr "to do with the lay life, "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an4.11:10.1"
msgid "Kummaggappaṭipanno so, "
msgstr "you’re on the wrong path, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:10.2"
msgid "Mohaneyyesu mucchito; "
msgstr "lost among things that delude. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:10.3"
msgid "Abhabbo tādiso bhikkhu, "
msgstr "Such a mendicant is incapable "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:10.4"
msgid "Phuṭṭhuṃ sambodhimuttamaṃ. "
msgstr "of touching the highest awakening. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an4.11:11.1"
msgid "Yo ca caraṃ vā tiṭṭhaṃ vā, "
msgstr "But one who, whether standing or walking, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:11.2"
msgid "Nisinno uda vā sayaṃ; "
msgstr "sitting or lying down, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:11.3"
msgid "Vitakkaṃ samayitvāna, "
msgstr "has calmed their thoughts, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:11.4"
msgid "Vitakkūpasame rato; "
msgstr "loving peace of mind; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:11.5"
msgid "Bhabbo so tādiso bhikkhu, "
msgstr "such a mendicant is capable "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:11.6"
msgid "Phuṭṭhuṃ sambodhimuttaman”ti. "
msgstr "of touching the highest awakening.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.11:11.7"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
